# Exercise 000 - Installing Minishift

1) Prepare the environment;

2) Download and uncompress Minishift executable [1];

3) Put the Minishift executable into you PATH;

4) Install Minishift;

5) Make your host able to run the oc command;

6) Enable auto complete for Minishift and oc commands;

[1] https://github.com/minishift/minishift/releases/download/v1.30.0/minishift-1.30.0-linux-amd64.tgz
